    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L straight-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through its six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing system. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and a crisp-shifting 6-speed manual transmission feeding a variable M differential lock. Recent service includes valve clearances and rod bearing inspection, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within factory spec. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, it exhibits minor patina consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast vehicle, prioritizing mechanical integrity and tactile feedback.",
